choices.text:
Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is a powerful thing.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

I love you because you make me feel complete.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is the most magical thing in the world.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is a feeling that is so strong that it can make you do anything.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is patient, love is kind. It does not envy, it does not boast, it is not proud. It is not rude, it is not self-seeking, it is not easily angered, it keeps no record of wrongs.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is a beautiful thing.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is a feeling that is experienced when two people care for each other deeply.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is a combination of care and affection.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Love is patient, love is kind. It does not envy, it does not boast, it is not proud. It is not rude, it is not self-seeking, it is not easily angered, it keeps no record of wrongs.

Write a sentence with ten words about love:

Being in love is one of the most beautiful things in the world.
